name: All About Olaf
content:
All About Olaf is a collaborative application created by students and alumni of St. Olaf College in Northfield, MN under the name StoDevX. It is inspired by the original 'All About Olaf', an iOS application created by Drew Volz as an independent project in 2014.

This version was written in the summer of 2016, led by Elijah Verdoorn and assisted by Hawken Rives and Drew Volz. The app is supported as well as published by the Student Government Association (SGA) web team, called the Oleville Development Team.
